Server IP: 89.243.244.157
If someone could try and connect i would be very grateful.
Thanks! :)
EDIT: Is the 'register a server' not working; or is it just not working for me? :|[br][size=1]Posted on: July 21, 2007, 06:58:18 AM[/size][hr]Wow lol..turns out some reason XP firewall was on. Fixed
